new IntWritable(25), new Text())).isNull();\n\n            Text closestValue = new Text();\n            assertThat(reader.getClosest(new IntWritable(25), closestValue)).isEqualTo(new IntWritable(30));\n            assertThat(closestValue.toString()).isEqualTo(\"thirty\");\n            assertThat(reader.getClosest(new IntWritable(25), closestValue, true)).isEqualTo(new IntWritable(20));\n            assertThat(closestValue.toString()).isEqualTo(\"twenty\");\n\n            IntWritable key = new IntWritable();\n            Text scannedValue = new Text();\n            assertThat(reader.seek(new IntWritable(30))).isTrue();\n            assertThat(reader.next(key, scannedValue)).isTrue();\n            assertThat(key).isEqualTo(new IntWritable(30));\n            assertThat(scannedValue.toString()).isEqualTo(\"thirty\");\n\n            IntWritable finalKey = new IntWritable();\n            reader.finalKey(finalKey);\n            assertThat(finalKey).isEqualTo(new IntWritable(40));\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void tFileStoresSortedRecordsAndNamedMetaBlocks() throws Exception {"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1844, "output": 1393, "cacheRead": 12288, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 15525, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777659693984, "responseId": "resp_0952c15e2030dbc00169f4ef2e833481949ae5d379ba4ee212"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_nquYnNO76s9wj9uwV5AtZRXI|fc_0952c15e2030dbc00169f4ef3818188194bdef1af0b2b73fd5", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully replaced 2 block(s) in tests/src/io.trino.hadoop/hadoop-apache/3.2.0-12/src/test/java/io_trino_hadoop/hadoop_apache/Hadoop_apacheTest.java."}], "details": {"diff": "     ...\n  20 import org.apache.hadoop.io.BytesWritable;\n  21 import org.apache.hadoop.io.DataInputBuffer;\n  22 import org.apache.hadoop.io.DataOut